# Valhalla's custom_files mount: the built routing tiles, the downloaded OSM extract,
# the .tar, and the admin/timezone DBs are all large and regenerable — keep them out
# of git. The one tracked exception is valhalla.json, a seed config the container
# deep-merges on first build (update_existing_config=True) to pre-raise
# max_exclude_polygons_length, so avoid zones route without hand-editing service limits.
tiles/*
!tiles/valhalla.json
